dct_title_s: Tokyô oyobi Yokohama fukkô chizu Jiji Shinpôsha.
dct_description_sm: Jiji Shinpô furoku. [Appendix to Jiji Shinpô.] "Fukkôkyoku kônin." [Authorized by Restoration Bureau.] In Japanese. North oriented toward right. Includes inset, legend and rebuilding plan list. On verso: 18 maps collectively entitled "Tokyô-shi sûyô chiku shindôro kakudaizu." Edited by Ishikawa Renjô. 1 map: col.; 74 x 91 cm., in wrapper 28 x 21 cm.
dct_rights_sm: This map is in the public domain.
